column7: I used to get a couple of dozen packages containing CDs each day, but these days receiving even one is something that happens once in a blue moon, a rare treat. It’s even more special when it contains a couple of releases from **Sex Clark Five**, one of my personal favorites. They sound like blurting out that thing you told yourself you weren’t going to say but felt good to say.
Still fresh all these years later
